These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, onion, garlic
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, mechanic, musician
1. the person eating blueberry is in an even position##4
2. the designer is on the left or right of the musician##3
3. the designer is the person eating onion##1
4. the person eating garlic is on the far left##1
5. the mechanic is the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | garlic | blueberry | onion |
| Job    | mechanic    | musician | designer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing, cooking
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, quad-bike, trike
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | rock-climbing | cooking | collecting |
| Transport   | trike    | quad-bike     | scooter        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, dancing, cooking
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, techno
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the fan of folk##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of folk##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | cooking     | dancing | traveling |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | folk     | techno  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, time-travel, fantasy
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, sailing, rugby
1. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | time-travel  | martial-arts  |
| Sport         | snowboarding  | sailing | rugby |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, reading, video-games
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, mexican, german
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the polish##2
2. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
3. the german is on the left of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | traveling   | video-games | reading    |
| Nationality   | mexican | german     | polish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, gardening, camping
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, rugby
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | gardening | camping | rock-climbing   |
| Sport   | rugby     | baseball    | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, disaster, family
3 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, pony
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is between the owner of the pony and the person watching family movies##2
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
4. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | scientific | disaster |
| Pet           | ferret         | bird         | pony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: grapes, plum, apricot
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, mouse
1. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the ferret and the person eating grapes##2
2. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person eating apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | plum | apricot | grapes |
| Pet    | ferret    | chinchilla | mouse     |

