.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, techno, electronic
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, ice-hockey, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the fan of classical##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the fan of techno##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic   | techno  | classical  |
| Sport         | soccer | ice-hockey | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, tea
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, lime, kiwi
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person eating kiwi is in an even position##4
3. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | water    | tea      | soy-milk |
| Food       | lime | kiwi | cauliflower   |

