.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, musician, mechanic
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, boat, snowmobile
1. the mechanic is on the right of the musician##1
2. the person driving the car is the social-worker##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is the mechanic##1
4. the mechanic is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job         | musician | mechanic | social-worker |
| Transport   | boat | snowmobile   | car |

