.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, malaysian, mexican
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, volleyball, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the mexican##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is the malaysian##1
