.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, puzzles, rock-climbing
3 different pets are kept: frog, bird, goat
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the owner of the bird##2
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the bird is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | rock-climbing | traveling |
| Pet     | frog    | goat  | bird   |

