2. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of funk##1
3. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
4. the person watching disaster movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | disaster     | animation |
| Music-Genre   | pop | funk | reggae    |

