.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, baking, skydiving
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, r&b, trance
1. the fan of trance is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the fan of r&b##1
4. the fan of techno is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | skydiving | reading   | baking |
| Music-Genre   | r&b   | techno | trance      |

