.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, 7up, lemonade
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, indian, dutch
1. the dutch is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
2. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | sprite | 7up | lemonade |
| Nationality   | indian   | dutch          | brazilian |

