.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, dog, lizard
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, skateboarding, baseball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the owner of the lizard is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Pet     | dog  | lizard   | hedgehog |
| Sport   | baseball | skateboarding | soccer       |

 